My bill with Mr. Gianforte will provide certainty to consumers by ensuring transparency in the calculations of drug costs. This bill will reign in pricing schemes that hide the true cost of medications and prevent their costs from skyrocketing!

PBMs are the middlemen who work with states, governments, and businesses to negotiate drug prices for the people on their health insurance plans. 3 organizations control 85% of the market. The lack of transparency into their practices has lead to the rising cost of prescriptions.
